-for-list\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">High-energy dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Social dogs</span><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d best-for-tag\">Owners looking for free exercise options</span></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">What to Bring</h4><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-list\"><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Leash (for entering/exiting)</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Water bowl</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Waste bags</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Toys</span></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bring-item\"><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-bag-check\"></i><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Treats</span></div></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d guide-section\"><h4 class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Pro Tips</h4><ul class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d tips-list\"><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Check park rules before visiting</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Keep your dog&#x27;s vaccinations up to date</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Supervise your dog at all times</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Clean up after your dog immediately</li><li class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">Respect other dogs and owners</li></ul></div></div><div class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d card-footer\"><button aria-expanded=\"false\" class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d expand-toggle\"><span class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d\">View guide</span><i class=\"jsx-a48b21ff5aa9f24d bi bi-chevron-down\">