,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-hero-copy\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-breadcrumbs\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Home\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"California Dog Parks\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"i\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"bi bi-chevron-right\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"strong\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"San Diego\\\"}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-eyebrow\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Coastal Canine Paradise\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h1\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":\\\"Indoor Dog Park In San Diego\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-chip-row\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-chip\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-label\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Off-Leash Beaches\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-value\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"5+\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-chip\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-label\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Avg Rating\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"chip-value\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"4.8 / 5\\\"}],\\\"$undefined\\\"]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"hero-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"San Diego is widely considered one of the most dog-friendly cities in America, home to legendary off-leash beaches and a massive network of canyon-side parks that celebrate the quintessential California lifestyle.\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"city-rich-description\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"0\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"San Diego is widely considered one of the most dog-friendly cities in America, home to legendary off-leash beaches and a massive network of canyon-side parks. The city’s dog identity is anchored by world-famous coastal access, notably Dog Beach in Ocean Beach, one of the nation’s first official off-leash shores. Unique \\\\\\\"canyon geography\\\\\\\" allows for large spaces like Fiesta Island and scenic Morley Field, where dogs roam varied terrain from sandy shorelines to shaded pine groves. Data from \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"https://www.sandiego.gov/park-and-recreation/parks/dog\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"_blank\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"noopener noreferrer\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"San Diego Parks\\\"}],null,\\\" shows over 15 designated off-leash areas. The culture extends to hospitality, with the brewery scene in North Park setting a national standard for canine inclusion on patios. For residents, our \\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",\\\"4\\\",{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/owner-resources\\\",\\\"target\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"rel\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-link\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"owner resources\\\"}],null,\\\" offer essential tips on navigating seasonal beach restrictions and finding the best \\\\\\\"after-play\\\\\\\" local grooming spots.\\\"]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"p\\\",\\\"1\\\",{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rich-description-paragraph\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"San Diego has also seen a surge in indoor enrichment centers for its active professional community. These facilities focus on canine fitness and cognitive training, offering treadmill sessions and scent-work courses. While the temperate climate rarely necessitates an \\\\\\\"indoor escape,\\\\\\\" these centers provide critical mental stimulation and controlled socialization, especially for puppies and rescue dogs. Membership models are popular, bundling daycare with weekend agility workshops. Hygiene and safety are top priorities, with facilities using hospital-grade sanitization and requiring comprehensive wellness records. By blending historic outdoor assets with modern, service-oriented enrichment, San Diego remains a gold standard for a dog-centric city. These venues ensure that pets remain well-balanced and safe, celebrating the California lifestyle year-round.\\\"]}]]}],\\\"$L31\\\",\\\"$L32\\\"]}],\\\"$L33\\\"]}]}],\\\"$L34\\\",\\\"$L35\\\",\\\"$L36\\\",\\\"$L37\\\",\\\"$L38\\\",\\\"$L39\\\",\\\"$undefined\\\",\\\"$L3a\\\",\\\"$L3b\\\",\\\"$L3c\\\",\\\"$L3d\\\",\\\"$L3e\\\"]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"2b:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"footer\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-new\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-grid\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-column\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h4\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"IndoorDogPark\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-links\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/about\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"About us\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/partners\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Partners\\\"}]}]]}]]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-column\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h4\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-heading\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Discover\\\"}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"ul\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"footer-links\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"Browse parks\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"li\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L12\\\",null,{\\\"href\\\":\\\"/how-it-works\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"How it works\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\