children\":[[\"$\",\"i\",null,{\"className\":\"bi bi-sparkles\"}],\" \",\"35+ centers verified\"]}]]}]\n33:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"city-hero-visual\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-card\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L42\",null,{\"src\":\"/images/cities/san-diego/hero.webp\",\"alt\":\"San Diego dog park landscape\",\"fill\":true,\"priority\":true,\"sizes\":\"(max-width: 768px) 100vw, 540px\",\"unoptimized\":true}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"hero-image-gradient\"}]]}]}]\n34:[\"$\",\"$L43\",null,{\"city\":\"San Diego\",\"state\":\"CA\"}]\n45:T613,Perched in San Diego, 24 Hour Dog Daycare delivers a dog park experience where energetic romps and mindful training feel perfectly balanced. Located in San Diego, CA, the park is tucked near 7686 Miramar Rd suite b, San Diego, CA 92126 and easy to reach for commuters and weekend adventurers alike. Guests rave about its 4.8-star average across 811 reviews, pointing to spotless grounds, intuitive traffic flow, and staff who remember every pup's quirks. The campus layers mature trees with long sight lines so guardians can relax while still keeping eyes on the action. Morning, afternoon, and twilight blocks are thoughtfully staggered to keep crowds light and vibes relaxed. Access runs on daily memberships, with flexible passes that welcome both spontaneous drop-ins and devoted regulars.\n\nExpansive turf runs, agility challenges, and shaded rest nooks stretch across the property so dogs can sprint, sniff, and reset without ever feeling crowded. 24 Hour Dog Daycare curates small-group play dates, confidence-building agility rotations, and gentle introductions for new rescues. Weekly enrichment labs, pop-up adoption drives, and local vendor markets keep San Diego's canine calendar fresh. Certified behavior teams circulate through each yard, coaching leash manners and offering quick progress reports. Health-forward protocols guide every visit at 24 Hour Dog Daycare, from double-gated e